com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel

Class StreetLevelProxyObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.ViewObject
      • com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel.StreetLevelProxyObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StreetLevelBuilding, StreetLevelLink

    public abstract class StreetLevelProxyObject
extends ViewObject
    Represents a base class for all street level objects rendered as part of the map. This interface serves as a generalization (or abstract base) for several more specified proxy object types, bundling their common properties.
